d:
I saw that the beacons got lit, so here's the TL for chapter three.

This one had a fair bit of dialogues going on, so I went for a more readable font than my previous uploads.
Likewise I translated the sfx at my own discretion trying to balance understanding the non-verbal action while also trying not to alter the original image too much.

Gotta love those umbilical cords at the end, 100% blood related pregnancy.

Have fun, ducklings.
